    </screenshot>
  </screenshots>
  <description>
    <p>A simple radio with a clear and concise interface. The application allows you to listen to radio stations from the website radio-browser.info. There is a function to search for stations, add favorite stations to favorites, as well as the ability to record them in mp3 format.</p>
  </description>
